gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: The vessel RangerIII is a passenger ferry that travels from the Keweenaw Peninsula to the Isle Royale National Park in Lake Superior. This vessel is equipped with a YSI 660 water quality instrument and the Vaisala WXT520 meteorological sensor. Ranger III main URL: http://www.mtri.org/rangeriii.html and additional site at: http://www.lakesuperiorwatermonitoring.org/ranger3/
